            "title": "DeepMind執行長：中國人工智能公司比西方落後6個月",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"DeepMind執行長：中國人工智能公司比西方落後6個月\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V9VEy05SlJB96PqYEhqsow--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-01/298cf030-f659-11f0-bbff-08da57dab794\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">DeepMind執行長：中國人工智能公司比西方落後6個月</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/deepmind%E5%9F%B7%E8%A1%8C%E9%95%B7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA%E5%B7%A5%E6%99%BA%E8%83%BD%E5%85%AC%E5%8F%B8%E6%AF%94%E8%A5%BF%E6%96%B9%E8%90%BD%E5%BE%8C6%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-180957772.html",
